            "title": "Coexistence of morphologically similar bats (Vespertilionidae) on Madagascar: stable isotopes reveal fine-grained niche differentiation among cryptic species",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Melanie",
