            "title": "Species on the menu of a generalist predator, the eastern red bat (Lasiurus borealis): using a molecular approach to detect arthropod prey",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Elizabeth L.",
                    "lastName": "Clare"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Erin E.",
                    "lastName": "Fraser"
                },
                {
